{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A story about discovering anomalies, finding strange energy sources, and the intertwining of peculiar spaces. Get ready to uncover hidden stories, delve into a horrifying narrative and unveil the most fundamental truth! </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Outlying Island is a horror adventure puzzle game where players will uncover the truth behind mysterious events in a peculiar small island filled with eerie distortions and intertwined spaces.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966510/extras/top.jpg?t=1730256402\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You wake up on the shore, confused and with hazy memories, to find yourself trapped in a small island overtaken by the authorities. The place is filled with surreal, layered spaces and otherworldly creatures lurking around every corner. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966510/extras/start.gif?t=1730256402\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on the role of the female protagonist and follow her steps as she uncovers the truth behind the island\u2019s horrors while striving to escape its intricate web of mysteries! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966510/extras/explore.gif?t=1730256402\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But remember, those who stare into the abyss will find the abyss staring back at them, until they too become a part of it... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966510/extras/san.gif?t=1730256402\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2966510/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1730256402","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c